- Bumalik, ngayon!

183
00:20:49.122 --> 00:20:50.165
lumabas ka!

184
00:20:50.249 --> 00:20:52.918
Kapag natapos na ang lahat,
wala kang maaalala.

185
00:20:53.669 --> 00:20:55.254
Pigilan mo sila! I-block sila!

186
00:20:55.337 --> 00:20:57.839
Tila hindi ito nangyari.

187
00:21:44.344 --> 00:21:46.138
<i>Tandaan. Isang minuto lang ito.</i>

188
00:21:46.221 --> 00:21:47.472
<i>Diretso lang ang takbo!</i>

189
00:22:19.588 --> 00:22:21.256
Narito ang iyong allowance para sa buwang ito.

190
00:23:01.880 --> 00:23:02.714
Sang-ung.

191
00:23:03.215 --> 00:23:04.424
Kang Sang-ung!

192
00:23:04.925 --> 00:23:06.426
Uy. Sagutin mo ako.

193
00:23:06.510 --> 00:23:07.594
Kang Sang-ung!

194
00:23:08.095 --> 00:23:08.929
Sagutin mo ako.

195
00:23:09.513 --> 00:23:10.764
Please sagutin mo na lang ako.

196
00:23:11.598 --> 00:23:12.432
Kang Sang-ung.

197
00:24:20.542 --> 00:24:21.543
Min-suk.

198
00:24:46.067 --> 00:24:47.360
Sang-ung, seryoso...

199
00:24:48.528 --> 00:24:51.698
Kung kumilos ka nang walang ingat muli, sumusumpa ako,

200
00:24:53.658 --> 00:24:55.202
